      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with this beauty, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s running smoothly and looking great. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home where it\u2019ll be appreciated just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm super happy to chat and tell you more!",
      "price": 31500.0,
