    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Vanos, delivering a sharp throttle response and a screaming 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the suspension features refreshed bushings for precise lateral control. The cooling system has been proactively overhauled with a high-flow water pump. This is a robust driver\u2019s car with sorted mechanicals and exceptional turn-in characteristics, ready for the apex.",
